76766.「おおっ <cs_pchero>。\n ついに にっくき魔女ハバネロを\n 倒し:
Oh <cs_pchero>. At long last, Cabo, you have
defeated Witch Habanero!

76770.「ママうえさま しっかりカボ。\n いったい 何が あったのカボ？:
Mama Uesama, hold tight, kabo. What in the
world happened to you, Cabo?

76771.「私は 何者かに呪いで 魔女ハバネロに\n 姿を変えられ…… からい刺激を欲する:
I was cursed by someone to be the Witch Habanero, and in my lust for stimulation, I have transformed this country into a terrible
place...

76772.「……ありがとう。私は 甘党の魔女シュガー。\n あなたには お礼をしたいところ:
...Thank you. I am Witch Sugar with a sweet
tooth. I'd love to repay you, but first I have
to get this country back on track...

76773.「ママうえさまっ すごいカボ。\n スウィ～ツランドが 元通りになったカボ。\n:
Mama Uesama, what a caboose! Sweetsland is
back to normal. We can eat sweet treats again!

76774.「これも全部 <cs_pchero>が\n がんばってくれた おかげカボね。\n:
All of this is thanks to <cs_pchero>'s hard
work. I hope you will accept my thanks!

76775.「<cs_pchero>が 来てくれなければ\n この国は どうなっていたことか:
I don't know what would have happened to this
country if <cs_pchero> hadn't come along.
Thank you very much.

76777.「我が名は 辛党の神 カプサイ神なり！: My name is Capsai God, god of spiciness!

76778.「辛党の神……？\n それじゃ ママうえに 呪いをかけて\n 魔女ハバネロにした:
God of spicy food...? So it was you, Cabo, who
put a curse on Mama Ue and turned her into the
Witch Habanero?

76779.「ふふふ……。いかにも！\n 我が呪いが断ち切られるとは 思わなんだが\n これ:
Indeed! I never thought my curse would be
broken, but this is a pleasantly spicy kick.

76780.「だが この程度の刺激では 満足できぬ。\n こうなれば 我自身の手で\n この:
But this level of stimulation does not satisfy
me. I will turn this country into a land of
hot and spicy food with my own hands!

76781.「このまま 戦いを挑むのは危険です！\n 辛党の神を 甘く見ては いけません。\:
It is dangerous to fight like this! We must
not underestimate the god of spiciness. Let's
retreat once and for all!

76782.「ふふふ……。それでよい。\n 貴様たちの あがく様を見ながら\n この刺激を:
Hmmm... that's good. I'll enjoy the
stimulation of watching you wriggle...

76783.「ジャック……。\n 私は この国を元の姿に戻すため\n チカラを 使い果たして:
Jack I have exhausted my power to restore this
country to what it was.

76784.「しばらくの間 休まねばなりません。\n 後のことは あなたたちに まかせます…:
I must rest for a while. I'll leave the rest
to you...

76785.「……<cs_pchero>。ジャックたちに\n あなたのチカラを 貸してあげて:
...<cs_pchero>. Please lend Jack and his
friends your help. Please save our
country...............................

76786.「ママうえさま わかったカボ。\n おいらたちで カプサイ神の魔の手から\n こ:
Mama Uesama: Okay, Kabo. We will protect this
country from the evil hand of the Capsai God,
Kabo!

76787.「もう一度 キミのチカラを貸してほしいけど\n カプサイ神は とても 強そうだっ:
I wish I could have your help again, but the
Capsai God seemed so strong, Cabo.

76788.「だから おいらは あいつを倒す手がないか\n ミローレさんに 相談してみるカボ:
So I'm going to talk to Milore to see if there
is a way to defeat him. Until we find a way to
do that, I want you to wait!
